forkee.name: Rosetta
forkee.description: Video and Audio translation service powered by Google Cloud APIs.  Team Project for DeltaHacks VI

commits.message:
Change tests folder name to outputs

This folder will hold al program outputs
but not the original input files

Improved directory structure

- Now uses an input folder for mp4 files
  and an output folder for program outputs
- Added a translated transcript file in outputs
- generated files now contain input file name
Made s2t and t2s more modular
process updated to take in variables for mp4 file, input lang and target lang, 6 languages supported (en,fr,hi,es,cmn,ja)

Rosetta final edition

quick and simple translation, dub your favorite videos!
